      "props": {
        "text": "Filtered feed grafts the gallery's `select_filtered_cards` onto the syndication channel ‚Äî six new query knobs (`?consensus=`, `?quality=`, `?outcome=`, `?q=`, `?sort=`, `?limit=`) make \"subscribe to my bullish-consensus stream\" a one-URL operation in Feedly / n8n / Zapier. Sitemap is sitemaps.org 0.9 XML over public sims (priority 0.8 per `/share/<id>`, 0.7 per `/watch/<id>`), byte-deterministic via id-ascending sort, behind `ENABLE_SITEMAP=true`. Together they close the May-12 repo-actions batch entirely (5/5 resolved ‚Äî 3 redundant, 1 deferred, 2 = these PRs). Zero-new-deps streak: 20 consecutive PRs (#57 ‚Üí #82).",
        "variant": "body"
